OL,3,CWhat could England's route to the
OL,4,CWorld Cup final look like?
OL,6,FITV News Sports Editor Steve Scott
OL,7,Fruns through England's potential route
OL,8,Fto the final if the Three Lions are
OL,9,Fable to beat DR Congo on Wednesday
OL,11,FEngland is preparing to face the
OL,12,FDemocratic Republic of Congo in the
OL,13,Fknockout stages of the World Cup after
OL,14,Ftopping their group.
OL,16,FThomas Tuchel's side have at times
OL,17,Flooked off their top form, but after
OL,18,Fpicking up seven points in three
OL,19,Fmatches, they head into the knockout
OL,20,Fstages as a top seed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
