OL,3,CWhat could England's route to the
OL,4,CWorld Cup final look like?
OL,6,FITV News takes a look at the path the
OL,7,FThree Lions will need to negotiate if
OL,8,Fthey hope to make their third major
OL,9,Ftournament final in a decade.
OL,11,FAs they head to Atlanta, Thomas
OL,12,FTuchel's side know they will face
OL,13,Ftournament minnows DR Congo in the
OL,14,Fround of 32.
OL,16,FBut, despite their size, the central
OL,17,FAfrican nation should not be
OL,18,Funderestimated. Tuchel warned England
OL,19,Fwill be "punished" if the World Cup
OL,20,Fcontenders dare look beyond their
OL,21,Fknockout date with DR Congo.
OL,26,@{D@IOU{D@RO]
