OL,3,CWhat could England's route to the
OL,4,CWorld Cup final look like?
OL,6,FThe back-to-back European Championship
OL,7,Ffinalists wrapped up top spot in Group
OL,8,FL with Saturday's 2-0 win over already-
OL,9,Feliminated Panama at MetLife Stadium,
OL,10,Fwhere they are aiming to return for
OL,11,Fthe final on July 19.
OL,13,FJude Bellingham and Harry Kane struck
OL,14,Fas England avoided a tougher-looking
OL,15,Froute through the knockout stages and
OL,16,Fset up a tie against a third-placed
OL,17,Fside, with DR Congo later confirmed as
OL,18,FWednesday's round-of-32 opponent in
OL,19,FAtlanta.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
