OL,3,CWhat could England's route to the
OL,4,CWorld Cup final look like?
OL,6,FA mouth-watering meeting with co-hosts
OL,7,FMexico, or Ecuador at the Azteca,
OL,8,Fcould follow next Sunday, but Tuchel
OL,9,Fhas not entertained any talk about the
OL,10,Fpathway and potential opponents.
OL,12,F"It's possible, but there's a match,
OL,13,Fno? And there is only one match that
OL,14,Fwe can focus on and that is the next
OL,15,Fmatch," the England boss said.
OL,17,F"If we get carried away and start
OL,18,Ftalking and thinking about possible
OL,19,Fround of 16, we will just get
OL,20,Fpunished."
