OL,3,CWhat could England's route to the
OL,4,CWorld Cup final look like?
OL,6,FMexico topped their group that also
OL,7,Ffeatured South Africa, South Korea and
OL,8,FCzechia, while Ecuador managed to
OL,9,Frally after an opening defeat to Ivory
OL,10,FCoast, a draw with Curucao and a
OL,11,Fsensational win against Germany.
OL,13,FIf Mexico bests Ecuador - in a match
OL,14,Fhosted in Mexico City - the Three
OL,15,FLions face a blockbuster challenge at
OL,16,Faltitude against one of the World Cup
OL,17,Fco-hosts.
OL,19,FQuarterfinal
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
