OL,3,CWhat could England's route to the
OL,4,CWorld Cup final look like?
OL,6,FEngland will avoid the top three world-
OL,7,Franked sides until the semifinals. If
OL,8,Fthey get to the quarterfinals, then
OL,9,FBrazil is likely to be the side at the
OL,10,Fopposite end of the pitch.
OL,12,FThe next side England would face off
OL,13,Fagainst would be the winner of the
OL,14,Fround-of-16 tie in New Jersey on July
OL,15,F5.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
