OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782836318
OL,3,CWhat could England's route to the
OL,4,CWorld Cup final look like?
OL,6,FThe last time England played Brazil in
OL,7,Fa World Cup quarterfinal was back in
OL,8,F2002, when Ronaldinho lobbed a free-
OL,9,Fkick over David Seaman, and Brazil
OL,10,Feventually went on to win the entire
OL,11,Fcompetition.
OL,13,FIf England make it to the semifinal,
OL,14,Fthey'll be up against Argentina - the
OL,15,Freigning champions.
OL,17,FOn paper, Lionel Messi's Argentina
OL,18,Flook to have a rather kind run at the
OL,19,Fsemifinal stage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
