OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782836318
OL,3,CWhat could England's route to the
OL,4,CWorld Cup final look like?
OL,6,FThe free-scoring Messi will have to
OL,7,Ftake his side past Cape Verde in the
OL,8,Fround of 32, either Australia or Egypt
OL,9,Fin the round of 16, and either
OL,10,FSwitzerland, Algeria, Colombia or
OL,11,FGhana in the quarterfinals.
OL,13,FEngland's biggest threat is likely to
OL,14,Fcome from either France or Spain, who
OL,15,Fare on course to meet in the
OL,16,Fsemifinals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
