OL,3,CWhat could England's route to the
OL,4,CWorld Cup final look like?
OL,6,FFrance are the world's top-ranked
OL,7,Fside, but pre-tournament favourites
OL,8,FSpain look the more likely opponents.
OL,9,FThey also beat Gareth Southgate's
OL,10,FEngland in the Euro 2024 final. Could
OL,11,Fhistory repeat itself?
